                  </div> <span class="acalog_archived_catalog"><span class="acalog_catalog_name">2015 Summer Session Catalogue</span></span> <span class="n1_archived acalog-highlight-ignore" style="padding: 0px">[ARCHIVED CATALOG]</span><br> <h1 id="acalog-content"> The Academic Program </h1> 
                  <div style="float: right">
                   <a rel="nofollow" href="/content.php?catoid=17&amp;navoid=492&amp;print" onclick="acalogPopup('/content.php?catoid=17&amp;navoid=492&amp;print', 'print_preview', 770, 530, 'yes');return false;" target="_blank" class="print_link acalog-highlight-ignore" alt="Text Version"><img src="img/print.gif" width="10" height="14" border="0" hspace="5" align="absmiddle" alt="Print-Friendly Page.">Print-Friendly Page</a>
